{
  "texts": [
    "Third, the system's advantage in real-time feedback may have some unintended consequences.",
    "Some learners become overly reliant on the system's corrections and fail to internalize language rules fully.",
    "In initial experiments, about 15% of users showed delayed improvement in their self-correction abilities.",
    "Additionally, the system's compatibility with low-specification devices is insufficient.",
    "In environments without GPU acceleration, response delays significantly increase, which limits the system's application in resource-constrained areas."
  ]
}